Keygen & OS 64 bit Fix reg!

it work fine on Win 7 64bit
thanks

Worked like a dream! Many thanks my friend. =)

Not to x64 users -- when you save the .reg file the only thing you change is to add the "Wow6432Node\" bit into the existing HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE lines. I'm probably the only one who got confused on this part, but I figured I'd post just in case. :D

Thanks again!
